Interface Criteria.Converter<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - provider-specific criteria: Hazelcast predicates, Mongo filters, or Ignite SQL strings.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CalculatingCriteria, FilterQueryBuilder, PredicateQueryBuilder, PredicateQueryBuilder
    Enclosing class:
    Criteria

    public static interface Criteria.Converter<T>
    Converts criteria to the native provider form. Implemented internally by storage providers.
